cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.SE

The paper discusses the use of blockchain technology to formalize and digitize farm records, which involves security and privacy concerns, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) the most likely category. The paper also mentions the use of instrumentation and automation to create electronic field records, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The use of blockchain also involves data management and storage, which falls under cs.DB (Databases). Finally, the paper discusses the potential impact of this technology on the agriculture industry, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
